{
  "stem": "27390.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the death of Pilsudski, things changed for the worse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pilsudski was considered a friend of the Jews because-- that's what I heard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When he was an running away from the [INAUDIBLE] police, he was hiding himself from the [INAUDIBLE] police, he was hidden by a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on, when Poland became independent, after 1918, he became the leader and he kept that it doesn't go to-- that anti-Semitism doesn't go too far.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But after he died, the-- the fascists came to the fore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember we lived in the center of the city and in Poland, on the 3rd of May is a national holiday.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know whether it still exists, this holiday, but before the war, it was a national holiday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on the 1st of May was the workers' holiday, like we were socialists came up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- the police used to on-- on-- on horses, they used to wait in the yard where we lived because they always expected trouble and they used to go out into the street to stop the riots and--",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was always-- there were always fights.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the 3rd of May, we were always told not to go out into the street because there was always trouble.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to pass the Jewish shops and-- and attack and break the windows and things like that, the fascists on the 3rd of May.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the 1st of May, there was always fights between the socialists and the fascists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were also told not to go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As children, we were told to keep indoors and this is the atmosphere that we were brought up.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
